                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="collapsePersonal" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="#headerPersonal" data-parent="#whoamiAcc">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                On a personal level I am an introverted, almost 30-year-old, with a small, close-knit group of friends
                and a love for learning and travelling. My hobbies include reading, playing video games, solving puzzles
                and being creative.  I am the youngest or second youngest (biologically and non-biologically) of the family.
                I was born in Pretoria and spend the first 5 years of my life living in Rooihuiskraal, after which we moved to
                small town Brits.  I completed my primary education at Generaal Hendrik Schoeman primary school and my high
                school education at Brits High School.
                Through out my live my mother has been a great source of inspiration and she has taught me <a href="#">values</a> to live by
                that will help me throughout my live.
            </div>
        </div>
