                </button>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseCareer" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="#headerCareer" data-parent="#whoamiAcc">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    I am currently at the beginning of what I consider my career marathon. During this marathon, a few wrong turns
